[
  {
    "content_id": 671401,
    "reference_id": 22318,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>為基督耶穌被囚的保羅：傳統上認為保羅是在羅馬的監獄中寫信，但也有可能他是在更早時期於以弗所寫信，那裡更接近腓利門在歌羅西的家（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"Phlm_BookIntro_Filament\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">腓利門書簡介</span>，「寫作的日期與地點」）。</p></li><li><p>提摩太是保羅最親密的同工之一（見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203514\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles\">提摩太</span>」簡介）。</p></li><li><p>同工：腓利門積極地參與在基督的事工中。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:1",
          "end_ref": "57001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 203514,
          "content_id": 650930,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles",
          "label": "提摩太",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671393,
    "reference_id": 22310,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:1–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001001-57001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅通常以簡短的介紹開始其書信，接著是問候以及為教會祈求恩惠與平安。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:1",
          "end_ref": "57001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671408,
    "reference_id": 22325,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這不僅是給腓利門的私人信件，同時也是給他的家人和教會的信。</p><ul><li><p>亞腓亞可能是腓利門的妻子。</p></li><li><p>當兵的：基督的僕人參與在戰爭中，必須準備好在反對者面前堅定站立（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:17\">弗6:10–17</a>）。</p></li><li><p>亞基布可能是腓利門的兒子（另於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:17\">西4:17</a>中提到）。</p></li><li><p>在你家的教會：早期基督徒在私人住宅中聚會（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">羅16:5</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19\">林前16:19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:15\">西4:15</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:2",
          "end_ref": "57001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671409,
    "reference_id": 22326,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>你們是複數形式，指的是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:2\">一章2節</a>中提到的所有人。</p></li><li><p>恩惠和平安分別代表傳統的希臘和希伯來問候語；恩惠和平安現在被理解為來自神的恩賜（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">羅5:1–2</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:3",
          "end_ref": "57001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671410,
    "reference_id": 22327,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:4–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001004-57001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在保羅的書信中，他常常為讀者們的信心和愛心感謝神，並提到他為他們禱告（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:8-Rom1:12\">羅1:8–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:4-1Cor1:9\">林前1:4–9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:11\">林後1:3–11</a>；對比<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:10\">加1:6–10</a>）。古希臘書信偶爾會在問候之後包含一個感恩的段落。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:4",
          "end_ref": "57001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671411,
    "reference_id": 22328,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我們因信靠基督而得救，並藉著對其他基督徒的愛而活出我們的救恩。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:5",
          "end_ref": "57001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671412,
    "reference_id": 22329,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這節經文可以有不同的翻譯方式。保羅暗示了因著神對腓利門的恩典，腓利門應該仁慈對待阿尼西謀（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:10\">1:10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:17-Phlm1:19\">17–19</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:6",
          "end_ref": "57001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671413,
    "reference_id": 22330,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001008-57001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅向腓利門提出請求，是因腓利門是以仁慈和有愛心的人聞名（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:5-Phlm1:7\">1:5–7</a>）。保羅本可以憑藉他作為基督使徒的權柄來要求他，但出於愛，保羅選擇了請求而非命令。</p></li><li><p>像我這有年紀的保羅：保羅訴諸於對年長者的尊重以及他為基督耶穌作囚犯的身份，來增加基督徒同工對他的尊敬。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:8",
          "end_ref": "57001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671394,
    "reference_id": 22311,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>展現恩慈（譯註：和合本未譯出此句子）：在羅馬世界中，逃跑的奴隸可能會受到嚴厲的對待，如鞭打、烙印，甚至被處決，這些懲罰都取決於主人的決定。</p></li><li><p>阿尼西謀是保羅的屬靈兒子，因為他透過保羅的事工成為信徒。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:10",
          "end_ref": "57001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671395,
    "reference_id": 22312,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>阿尼西謀的意思是「有用的」。</p></li><li><p>從前與你沒有益處（字面意思是<em>無用的</em>）<span>……</span>都有益處：這可能是一個雙關語（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:20\">1:20</a>；譯註：「得著快樂」的原文與阿尼西謀一名的原文相似）。阿尼西謀現在正在服事他人並傳揚福音。<span>他最於成為了他名字所代表的意義的人</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:11",
          "end_ref": "57001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671396,
    "reference_id": 22313,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:13–14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001013-57001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅暗示他希望腓利門選擇釋放阿尼西謀，並讓他作為保羅的助手（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:21\">1:21</a>）。基督徒的生命<span>是對上帝恩典甘心的回應</span>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">羅12:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">弗4:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:13\">西3:12–13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:13",
          "end_ref": "57001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671397,
    "reference_id": 22314,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>他暫時離開你（字面意思是<em>他離開了</em>）：這可能是委婉地說他逃跑了，以避免直接提及阿尼西謀的過錯。</p></li><li><p>或者是叫你永遠得着他：這句話暗示神<span>在祂的護理中安排了這一切</span>，引導阿尼西謀蒙恩得救。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:15",
          "end_ref": "57001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671398,
    "reference_id": 22315,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然阿尼西謀在法律上仍然是腓利門的奴隸，但腓利門必須把他視為親愛的弟兄，並致力於他的福祉。</p><ul><li><p>這也不拘是按肉體說，是按主說：基於基督裡的弟兄情誼，如今必須在自然和屬靈的層面上<span>徹底改變他們之間整體的關係</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:16",
          "end_ref": "57001016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671399,
    "reference_id": 22316,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>阿尼西謀可能在逃跑時從腓利門的家中偷了一些東西，或者留下了一筆需要償還的債務。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:18",
          "end_ref": "57001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671400,
    "reference_id": 22317,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>保羅以他的簽名來確保他的承諾。他通常是口述信件<span>，由書記代寫</span>；但就像在此處，他偶爾會親自寫下一些內容。</p></li><li><p>你自己：確切的說，這指的是他的得救。腓利門虧欠保羅的遠超過阿尼西謀可能虧欠他的。<span>至於腓利門是否是直接或間接因著保羅的傳道而歸信，則不得而知</span>（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">西1:7</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:19",
          "end_ref": "57001019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671402,
    "reference_id": 22319,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>望你使我<span>……</span>因你得快樂：或<em>讓我得到這個好處</em>；希臘文onaimēn（「恩惠，好處」）可能是以阿尼西謀名字而說的雙關語，因這個名字的意思是「有益的」（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:11\">1:11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:20",
          "end_ref": "57001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671403,
    "reference_id": 22320,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>必過於：保羅可能是在暗示他希望看到阿尼西謀獲得釋放（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:13-Phlm1:14\">1:13–14</a>），或者他可能只是表達他對腓利門的仁慈有信心。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:21",
          "end_ref": "57001021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671404,
    "reference_id": 22321,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>保羅預先請求預備一間客房，以表明他有意前來拜訪</span>，<span>這進一步強化了他對腓利門善待阿尼西謀的請求。</span>當他來訪時，他將能親眼看見阿尼西謀受到怎樣的對待。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:22",
          "end_ref": "57001022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671406,
    "reference_id": 22323,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以巴弗是歌羅西本地人，他是第一位將福音帶給腓利門和他的家人的人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">西1:7</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">4:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:23",
          "end_ref": "57001023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671405,
    "reference_id": 22322,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:23–25",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001023-57001025",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅通常以他人對收信人的問候和祝福來結束他的信件。參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7-Col4:18\">歌羅西書四章7至18節</a>；保羅寫給歌羅西信徒和腓利門的書信可能是由推基古和阿尼西謀同時帶到歌羅西的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:23",
          "end_ref": "57001025",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:25"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 671407,
    "reference_id": 22324,
    "title": "腓利門書 1:24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "57001024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這些人在歌羅西書的結尾也被提起<span>（</span><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10\">西4:10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:14\">14</a><span>）</span>。</p></li><li><p>同工：他們協助保羅傳揚福音。</p></li><li><p>馬可：見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203502\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles\">約翰馬可</span>」簡介。</p></li><li><p>亞里達古是保羅多年來忠實的同工（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:29\">徒19:29</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:4\">20:4</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:2\">27:2</a>）。</p></li><li><p>底馬是一位同工，後來離棄了保羅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">提後4:10</a>）。</p></li><li><p>路加：見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203504\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles\">路加</span>」簡介。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "57001024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:24",
          "end_ref": "57001024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "PHM 1:24"
        }
